{"type":"message","id":"c40e1d88","parentId":"8f81c760","timestamp":"2026-04-14T22:25:13.950Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0un1gel8y4ur_2","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"0a3d09d5a64252784c96e620690bce343168c6b4dba69ffeb83a6dcc0ecb2b99\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-14.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 28,\n      \"score\": 0.7780012962501243,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7780012962501243,\n      \"snippet\": \"# 2026-04-14 — Orbis Daily Log\\n\\n## 16:34 UTC — Heartbeat Check\\n- sessions_list: GATEWAY TIMEOUT (ws://127.0.0.1:18789)\\n- subagents: 1 active (Telegram send task — SIGKILL'd / unknown 'send' cmd)\\n- Pipeline: DEGRADED\\n- Action: Monitoring. No alert to Khuowgn yet. Will retry next cycle.\\n\\n## 16:37 UTC — Telegram Delivery Reroute\\n- **Issue:** Subagent (c2d275a5) failed — no Telegram tool in subagent runtime\\n- **Action:** Spawned planner subagent (63bb70ce) to handle Telegram delivery\\n- **Thread binding:** Unavailable via webchat — used run mode instead\\n- **Blocker:** cron:e7885813 still needs review/disable; Telegram delivery unstable since 07:18 UTC\\n\\n## 17:32 UTC - Prior Instance Flag Cleared\\n-\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-04-14.md#L1-L28\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-04-14.md#L1-L28\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"07cdf349780f84851f44e5ab68761cdbe5f6e4a62559b8fbf3f07e739935bf41\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/dtlx-context.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 46,\n      \"score\": 0.7339142121539107,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7339142121539107,\n      \"snippet\": \"# AHV DTLX Project Context\\n\\n_Last updated: 2026-04-12 by Orbis_\\n\\n## ⚠️ CRITICAL — System Architecture\\n\\n**DTLX và QLHV là 2 hệ thống DÙNG CHUNG database:**\\n\\n```\\nDTLX (MASTER) ─────────────────── QLHV (SUBSYSTEM)\\n   Hệ thống chính                    Tách ra c